title: Disneys ESPN withdraws content from YouTube
text:
Disney's ESPN withdraws content from YouTube 
Reuters Saturday 24th October, 2015 
YouTube unveils their new paid subscription service at the YouTube Space LA in Playa Del Rey, Los Angeles, California, United States October 21, 2015....
